Description: Therapeutic Massage Therapy with goals of holistic relaxation, pain management, and stress relief ~ integrating elements of Myofascial Release, Swedish, Trigger Point Therapy, …Learn more about Behr Bodywork, Opens a popupSpecialtiesTherapeutic Massage Therapy with goals of holistic relaxation, pain management, and stress relief ~ integrating elements of Myofascial Release, Swedish, Trigger Point Therapy, Neuromuscular Therapy, Deep Tissue, Sports Massage, Thai Massage, Craniosacral Therapy, and Shiatsu into the session to help relax and rejuvenate.HistoryEstablished in 2014.I completed my massage training on the beaches of Costa Rica at The Costa Rica School of Massage Therapy (CRSMT) and have been practicing professional bodywork for over 5 years.At CRSMT, instructors from all over the world flew in to instruct my class of 20 on a specialized modality of bodywork for a semester at a time.I've been trained in a Swedish style of Massage, incorporating elements of Myofascial Release, Trigger Point/Neuromuscular Therapy, Deep-Tissue Massage, Thai Massage, Craniosacral Therapy, and Shiatsu into the session depending on what you need at that time.After CRSMT, I completed the 250 hour apprenticeship in Mindful Expressionism at the Berkana Institute here in Denver where I specialized in a focussed, artful, and meditative approach to bodywork.Over the years and through this journey, I've been taught by various teachers to seek mindfulness in action and practice, and I will always strive to stay present with you during our session together.Meet the Business Owner

Description: We are a collective of boutique marijuana dispensaries in Colorado. Greenhouse grown craft cannabis, edibles & concentrates made with(21+) #eufloraco @eufloracoEuflora is one of …Learn more about Euflora, Opens a popupSpecialtiesWe are a collective of boutique marijuana dispensaries in Colorado. Greenhouse grown craft cannabis, edibles & concentrates made with(21+) #eufloraco @eufloracoEuflora is one of Colorado's premiere recreational cannabis dispensaries with 4 locations in Denver & Aurora, Colorado.It is the goal of our knowledgeable and trained budtenders to offer each customer guidance in choosing the right strain or product to meet their needs. Informally dubbed "The Apple Store of Cannabis," we offer a unique and comfortable experience, free from the confinements of a traditional dispensary. Our chic modern look combined with technology driven layout allows our customers to browse freely. At Euflora you can see, touch and even sample the aromas of the very products you wish to purchase. It is an experience unlike any other dispensary and one which makes our customers feel immediately at home. Come experience the difference that sets us apart.HistoryEstablished in 2014.Euflora opened our first store in Denver, Colorado on April 2, 2014 and is currently the one and only dispensary located on the 16th Street Pedestrian Mall.In October, 2014, Euflora was honored to be the very first Recreational Cannabis store to open in Aurora, Colorado. This dispensary (Gunclub Rd.) is unique because it's in an old bank building; our owner likes to say, "banks wouldn't lend to us, so we started buying banks". Our 2nd Aurora store opened shortly thereafter (Buckley Rd.). We are thrilled to have just opened our 4th Dispensary at the Historic 3D Cannabis Center in Denver, which on January 1, 2014 was the first place on Earth to sell recreational cannabis. Stop by to see the largest cannabis cultivation viewing room in Colorado! The tour is free to anyone 21 and over. Euflora continues to grow and expand to serve the needs of our loyal customers. Looks for more Euflora stores in Colorado and beyond as Cannabis Legalization spreads across the nation.Meet the Business Owner

Drawing on years of experience serving patients, we embraced the opportunity to help a much larger community enjoy the benefits of cannabis. We spent a year reinventing our approach to serve the diverse needs and experiences of the state's cannabis consumers. Ajoya is the result of this transformation.Ajoya celebrates individual experience and personal freedom. Description: Quality, affordable medical marijuana in Boulder, Colorado.Learn more about Terrapin Care Station, Opens a popupSpecialtiesQuality, affordable medical marijuana in Boulder, Colorado.HistoryEstablished in 2010.Terrapin Care Station began in 2010 and has provided quality product at an affordable price ever since. In October 2011, Terrapin Care Station became one of the first licensed medical marijuana dispensaries within the State of Colorado and on February 18, 2014, they opened the first retail marijuana dispensary, open to anyone over the age of 21, within the City of Boulder, located at 1795 Folsom St. (open daily from 9 a.m. - 6:45 p.m.). Their newest recreational location at 11091 E. Mississippi Ave. in Aurora, CO is open 8 a.m. - 10 p.m. daily. With accessible recreational locations in Aurora and Boulder and a discreet medical location in south Boulder (5370 Manhattan Cir. #104), Terrapin Care Station offers all customers safe, affordable, and quality cannabis. Their plants are lovingly grown in soil, not just a nutrient solution, giving them stronger flavors for a more enjoyable experience.Meet the Business Owner
